Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}(喜歡)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 班裡養的兔子死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吃了什麼不好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們幹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天看到三個女生聚在兔籠前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 是小梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小梅說它什麼都吃 要給它吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說不要 但她非要給
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(橘)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什麼也沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 為什麼這樣對我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 軟糖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 不要開著龍頭打洗髮乳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掛了風鈴 有夏天的感覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 掛得晚了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候都不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼事都是只要開始了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歌詞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你也要吃飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心點兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 那個陰暗女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多少年沒有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝沒聽見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不要問些失禮的問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是十六年都沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友也十六年沒交過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後估計還會一年年持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能稱為朋友的人 至今為止倒是有過幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我已經發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有朋友 也只會傷害到自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 昨天那種情況真是太氣人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說清野的女生都是巨乳 還很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才那麼興奮趕過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果女生都是衝著大和來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種好像不關你事兒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可愛的那個女孩兒絕對盯上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別小看我中西的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你和那女孩兒互留手機號了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 咋回事 why
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼為什麼呀 只是初次見面又不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼可愛的女孩兒向你發出那麼熱情的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我覺得和其他女孩子沒什麼區別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校最受歡迎的男人就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家憧憬的 又對大家親切的黑澤大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在諷刺我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子在你眼裡不會全部都一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒覺得她們有優劣之分…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天晚上去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你打電話你沒接呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和清野高中的人一起吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種場合怎麼不叫上麻美一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 下次一定告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 下次大家一起去K歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼呢 這個動作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連麻美 都想要從我這裡奪走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美她可是我的真命天使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是胸部太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是只看胸部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有只喜歡胸部 麻美她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘梅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和我是同班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來都那副樣子 不說一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概沒人聽過她的聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道她在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這種人最沒招了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早操究竟為什麼而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 你們兩個…景色很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態中西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遮就別穿這麼短的裙子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 別欺負人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在提醒她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一遮呢 反倒會引起別人的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是你在邀請人看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你太色了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟色老頭似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天和清野的女生一起吃飯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聯誼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 吃個飯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾 也和我們一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 我會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 很少見的及膝裙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了和別人不同 引人注意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿這種裙子的會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 什麼呀 是橘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 中西 你幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑澤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑澤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次每次 都說不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這又是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別狡辯了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是中西做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹勢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把腦袋摔壞了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘…梅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去社團啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 什麼態度呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己多了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\frz12.278\pos(962,155)\3c&HDAE8F7&\4c&HDAE8F7&\c&H59616A&}踢無辜的人太可惡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\frz12.278\4c&HDAE8F7&\c&H59616A&\pos(1139,629)\3c&HB7C1CE&}去道歉！笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘梅同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉？為什麼你要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我朋友做錯了事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉你裙子的那個人叫中西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是和你一個班的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 反正我們也沒有在班裡講過話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙雖然很囂張 但是沒什麼惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是會讓人討厭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同學 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我踢錯了人真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不過你的態度一下子轉變得那麼快…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得橘同學很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是覺得捉弄我很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到橘同學是我喜歡的那種有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所說的有趣是指… 要怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用解釋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就吃這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得太多會壞肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來交換電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的交換電話是指交換郵箱 不是手機本身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你踢飛的時候 你的手受傷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的傷只用這麼小的創可貼治癒不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要的話就和我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被討厭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久都沒和學校的人講話了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給了我手機號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是擁有那樣微笑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也不會給他打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力酥皮餅出鍋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛出爐的巧克力酥皮餅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多捧場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不是發燒了吧 臉這麼紅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉才沒紅 也沒有發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這些東西 請算賬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜食也都放在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請分開放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 可以的話 請根據個數來包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收您2000日元 找零950日元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒算錯 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 來幫我弄一下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 「我回來了」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想這些有的沒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正到頭來還是會被背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說梅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有給我打電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可一直在等你電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說過要給你打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就聯繫一下下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說討厭跟朋友聊天什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我家和打工的地方的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人總是會輕易地背叛別人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校這地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「必須把某個人當靶子耍的混蛋集結地」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像過家家似的 裝作關係很好的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦情況不對 就會置身事外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想跟那樣的人成朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是所有人都那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友這種東西 對我來說不是必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到大和了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這發什麼呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒去唱K吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是說好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去沒事嗎 只限萌妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中西你真是的 總是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群女孩子不是會熱鬧點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這種爛借口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只要有小麻美就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉呢 弄到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人 是麵包店的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道從麵包店到這裡的回家路線恰巧跟我相同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 從剛剛開始就一直在那裡站著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還往我這看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是碰巧 是跟蹤的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 快接電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻美最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 你來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先接個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰打的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我是橘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點梅 你現在在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三丁目的便利店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上來 待在那裡別走開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的那個男的 是我打工的地方的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天關門了之後就跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直跟到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟了多長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多35分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是跟蹤狂麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也聯繫不上 能商量的人也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑澤君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑過來的 熱死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的我都明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道這是什麼樣的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我的初…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:50.95,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(976,429)}「接吻」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼沒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:13.31,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\be3}慣れきた表情の　冷たい朝が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:13.31,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}喜歡能看到你熟悉表情的清冷早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:19.08,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}あからさまなった意図みせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:19.08,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}如此直率地向我表明心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:25.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}予言のような空の色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:25.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}天空的顏色如預言般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:31.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}そんなに意地悪しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:31.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}不要這樣的捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:36.98,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}笑った薄い唇に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:36.98,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}你的薄唇邊掛著微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:42.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}傾く影を追いかけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:42.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}我追尋著你傾斜的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:48.94,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}君さえもわからないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:48.94,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}即使我還對你一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:57.26,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}頼りない　もっと抱きしめて放題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:57.26,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}雖然不可靠 但請自由地擁抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:00.58,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}重ねていくいつもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:00.58,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}總會有許多的交匯處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.75,0:23:08.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}頼りないぐらい　不器用なslow dance
